    statistics-manager org.opendaylight.controller.md.statistics.manager.impl StatListenCommitGroup Class is a NotifyListener for GroupStatistics and DataChangeListener for Config/DataStore for Group node. All expected (registered) GroupStatistics will be builded and commit to Operational/DataStore. DataChangeEven should call create/delete Group in Operational/DS
